power Function
Raises a number to the power of another number.
Syntax
power(number, power)
Arguments
number Literal value or measure field that you want to raise to the specified power.
power Literal value or measure field that is the power that you want to raise the specified number to.
title: Using Power Function in Salesforce CRM Analytics
